{"tid":1143282,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【大師專訪】沈振盈：2019年恒指見萬六點","createTime":"2019-05-07T15:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T01:48:51.000Z","uid":232237,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db0cc2d6cc9a5fdf5749f250857a90786883ca9a","tid":1143282,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"不經不覺，著名股評人沈振盈被冠以「燈神」稱號逾10年，原來他對這稱號只是忍受而非接受，自覺受盡「網絡欺凌」。今年初大升市時，網絡又為他起了新名號－「沈判日」，調侃他的淡市預測，誰知大半年恒指真的跌了5千點，「沈判」判詞或成真。他帶點不平說：「如果經常錯，點會咁多人睇、咁多Fans追逐呢？」<br />\n<br />\n今年是沈大師的「轉角市」1月，他出席「城市論壇」後稱股市近頂，自己「一股不留」，各大網絡討論區隨即湧出「明燈出動」、「與沈對賭」、「即刻瞓身」或「長期唱淡，總有次中」等留言，並出現了「沈判日」、「一股不留」等揶揄他的網絡潮語。<br />\n<br />\n下半年的投資建議，沈大師表示，「一定係揸現金、存定期，唔好買基金！」他認為現時銀行定期年息有兩厘多，不遜於公用股的股息。記者嘀咕：「滙控(005)有5厘息！」沈大師即指出，滙控股價由年初高位86元，到8月底只剩約70元，已經跌了近兩成！<br />\n<br />\n沈大師斷言股災已經出現，他本人身體力行堅持熊市策略高位沽貨。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6月跌穿三萬點，「我便確定我啱！」</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535644719_c64b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535644719_c64b.jpg&h=8b5e556e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535644719_c64b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535644719_c64b.jpg&h=8b5e556e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535644719_c64b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535644719_c64b.jpg&h=8b5e556e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535644719_c64b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535644719_c64b.jpg&h=8b5e556e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58627243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58627243&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8S8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=b3123f7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58627243&h=28a3680d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58627243</a>"},{"pid":"b61ea7d8456651d3f95dafb894d7a0686adc0ecf","tid":1143282,"uid":113373,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半<br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c32c219d5eb1e9558e02246a7201beaaf63a00fc","tid":1143282,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaff60ba3736694a50d877e0a0ab38be67096898","tid":1143282,"uid":118648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"出少句聲當幫忙啦 聽日又碌返上三萬㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4965c12d7170e73f8f429abe3a222d57f6ab11b1","tid":1143282,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n